<H3> <TI>   Minister Supports China's Entry Into GATT </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Minister Supports China's Entry Into GATT </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1506100894 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 
GMT 15 Jun 94 </F>

