<F P=102>   NC1506172994 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 15 Jun 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1506172994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The UN forces this afternoon handed over to the 
Lebanese Army four Iraqis who had been taken prisoner by the 
Israeli occupation troops in Jordan [as heard]. 
  At 1600 today, the Israeli occupation troops released four 
Iraqis, who were taken prisoners in the Jordan Valley four 
months ago, at Jisr al-Hamra' in Tyre. The Israeli soldiers 
untied the prisoners and ordered them to walk toward the 
liberated area. The released Iraqis sought the help of the 
Finnish contingents in al-Hamra'. 
  Following contacts the Finnish contingents made with the 
Lebanese authorities, the Iraqis were handed over to the 
Lebanese Army. 

</TEXT>

