<H3> <TI>   Terror Suspects Detained; Explosives Seized </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Terror Suspects Detained; Explosives Seized </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1506184694 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1800 GMT 15 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1506184694 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 15 Jun (MENA)--State Security Intelligence 
agents have arrested 79 terrorist elements in sweeps carried out 
in a number of southern governorates. 
  According to an Interior Ministry statement, the sweeps led 
to the confiscation of five explosive charges weighing 0.5 kg 
each, 10 sticks of gelignite, seven electric detonators, 14 
loaded ammunition clips, bullets of various calibers, a 
mini-truck with Suhaj license plate No. 10426 belonging to 
fugitive terrorist Mahmud Salim, and a number of documents. 
State Security investigators are interrogating the detained 
terrorists and searching for other individuals believed to have 
links with them. 

</TEXT>

