<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Meets With Libyan Foreign Secretary </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Meets With Libyan Foreign Secretary </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1506183494 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
15 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1506183494 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 14 June brother President Yasir 'Arafat received 
the secretary of the General People's Committee for Foreign 
Affairs of the fraternal Libyan Jamahiriyah. President 'Arafat 
received at the meeting a message from his brother Mu'ammar 
al-Qadhdhafi, leader of the al-Fatih revolution. 

</TEXT>

