BFN 

  [Excerpt] The rebel movement today released UN relief 
workers and the two barges which the movement had taken over in 
the Jonglei area, after emptying them of their cargoes. This 
was reported to SUNA by Dr. Muhammad Ahmad al-Aghbash, the 
relief commissioner general. He said the two barges were 
currently on their way back to Malakal. [passage omitted] 

