<H4>    Meets With Official Spokesman </H4>

<F P=102> EA1406152594 Omdurman Republic of Sudan Radio Network in 
Arabic 2245 GMT 13 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA1406152594 </F>
<F P=104>  Omdurman Republic of Sudan Radio Network </F>
