<H3> <TI>   U.S. Ambassador Uninjured in Road Accident </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    U.S. Ambassador Uninjured in Road Accident </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1406141494 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 1350 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1406141494 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuwait KUNA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Kuwait City, 14 Jun (KUNA) -- The car of Ryan 
Crocker, U.S. ambassador to Kuwait, was involved in a road 
accident today. Two persons sustained slight injuries as a 
result of this accident. 
  A statement released by the U.S. Embassy, a copy of which 
was 
received by KUNA, said that "the ambassador was not injured in 
this accident; while two other persons, one of whom was the 
ambassador's driver, sustained slight injuries." 
  The statement indicated that the accident happened at 1000 
local time at Roundabout No. 2. 

</TEXT>

