  [Text] Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin yesterday sent PLO 
Chairman Yasir 'Arafat a letter in which he replies to the three 
messages sent by the PLO chairman over recent days. The Rabin 
response was sent to 'Arafat through a Palestinian mediator. 
