Commander Major Tahsin, Captain Khamis, and First Lieutenant 
[name indistinct] from al-'Awja village, who is a relative of 
criminal Husayn Kamil--were killed in the attack. The contents 
of the post were destroyed and other mercenaries received 
various wounds. The attacker was killed in a shootout with a 
group of mercenaries of the special security on the main street 
opposite the garage. 

