Ja'ja' [leader of the dissolved Lebanese Forces Party]; (?Kamil) 
Hanna Karam; Ghassan Antoine Tuma; Antonios Ilyas Ilyas, alias 
Antonios Ilyas 'Ubayd; (?Tony) 'Ubayd; Jean Yusuf Shahin, alias 
