<F P=100> Libya </F>
<H3> <TI>   African Leaders Arrive for Regional Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    African Leaders Arrive for Regional Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Burkina Faso's Campaore Arrives </H4>

<F P=102> LD1506193494 Tripoli JANA in Arabic 1845 GMT 15 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1506193494 </F>
