<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Receives European Troika Ambassadors </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Receives European Troika Ambassadors </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1806174694 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
18 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1806174694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] President 'Arafat, president of the state of 
Palestine and chairman of the PLO Executive Committee, this 
morning received ambassadors of the European troika under the 
chairmanship of the Greek charge d'affairs, the ambassador of 
Belgium, and the ambassador of the European Commission. 
  President 'Arafat and the ambassadors discussed the need for 
providing necessary means of support by building the 
infrastructures of the Palestinian national authority in the 
Palestinian self-rule areas. He urged them to provide the 
necessary funds to start the rebuilding needed for these 
infrastructures. 

</TEXT>

