<F P=103> TA1906065294 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Nabil Sha'th, who arrived in Gaza last week, 
will meet tomorrow in East Jerusalem with members of the 
Palestine National Authority [PNA] from the West Bank. Today he 
will meet with Major General Amnon Shahaq to discuss issues left 
unresolved in the Israel-PLO peace treaty. Mark Weiss reports: 
  [Begin Weiss recording] All the members of the PNA from the 
West Bank have been invited to tomorrow's meeting at the Orient 
House in East Jerusalem. These include Bethlehem Mayor Ilyas 
