<H3> <TI>   `Finance Minister' al-Nashashibi Arrives in Jericho </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Finance Minister' al-Nashashibi Arrives in Jericho </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1906113494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 19 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1906113494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Muhammad Zuhdi al-Nashashibi, the autonomy's 
finance minister, crossed the Allenby Bridge and arrived in 
Jericho a short time ago. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports 
that al-Nashashibi, a member of the Palestinian Authority and 
the PLO Executive Committee, will be the minister in charge of 
economic issues in the autonomous areas. Upon arriving in 
Jericho, he stated that he came to organize the economy of the 
population of the territories. 

