their homes. This follows the failure on the part of these 
forces to realize their strategic military ambitions of 
occupying our territory and forcing our people in democratic 
Yemen to submit to the adventurist authority of Sanaa by force 
of arms. 
  Also since this morning the forces of the ruling military 
regime have continued their attempts to advance towards Aden, 
but our defending Armed Forces repulsed them and prevented any 
advance by these enemy invading forces. Battles are continuing 
on all fronts following the refusal by the ruling military 
regime in Sanaa to listen to the voice of good sense and logic. 
Instead, it chooses to press on with its adventurist hostile 
operations against our people. 

