<H3> <TI>   Ben Ali Holds Talks With Namibian President </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ben Ali Holds Talks With Namibian President </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1606143194 Tunis Tunisian Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1300 GMT 16 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1606143194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tunis Tunisian Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] President Zine El Abidine Ben Ali held talks 
this morning at the Carthage Palace with President Sam Nujoma of 
Namibia within the framework of the official visit which the 
Namibian president is making to our country after the OAU 
summit. [passage omitted] 
  The official spokesman [for the presidency] said that during 
these talks President Zine El Abidine Ben Ali and President Sam 
