<H3> <TI>   Peres on Postponement of Christopher Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Peres on Postponement of Christopher Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1906200494 Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew 1930 GMT 19 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA1906200494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv IDF Radio </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres 
said this evening that the postponement of Secretary of State 
Warren Christopher's visit does not point to a deadlock in 
negotiations with Syria. Christopher wants a little more 
progress to be achieved before the visit, and he apparently 
decided to wait a little while longer, Peres said. 

</TEXT>

